    "title": "Aspose.BarCode Recognize Barcode Micro Application for .NET",
    "version": "25.6.0",
    "description": "Aspose.BarCode Recognize Micro Application is reliable barcode recognition CLI tool, written in managed C#, it allows to quickly and easily recognize barcodes of various types. Aspose.BarCode Recognize supports most established barcode standards and barcode specifications. It has the ability to work with multiple image formats including: BMP, GIF, JPEG, PNG, TIFF."
